Package: r3js
Type: Package
Title: WebGL-based 3D plotting in R using the three.js library
Version: 1.1.0
Author: Samuel H. Wilks
Maintainer: Samuel H. Wilks <sw463@cam.ac.uk>
Description: Provides R and javascript functions to allow WebGL-based 3D plotting in R using the three.js javascript library. Simple interactivity through roll-over highlighting and toggle buttons is also supported.
